ration notes appear.\r\n- For ongoing projects, update operations/runbook and operations context when cadence, trigger, or failure handling changes.\r\n\r\n## Open Tasks\r\n\r\n- task-0002: ��ʵ�� agent ��·��֤������ۡ��½ڡ���У��ܹ� QA [ready, high]\r\n\r\n## Open Next Actions\r\n\r\n- next-0001: ����ʵ agent ��������������� [open, medium]\r\n- next-0002: �ȴ��ĸ� watched builder/QA task-link �ص����������� [open, medium]\r\n\r\n## Dynamic Context for Phase: validation\r\n\r\n- No phase-specific dynamic context recorded yet.\r\n\r\n","metadata":{"output":"# Agent Handoff Guide: ����С˵���� Agent ������ (xuanhuan-novel-workflow)\r\n\r\n## Project Identity\r\n\r\n- Root: D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\xuanhuan-novel-workflow\r\n- Type: workflow\r\n- Mode: ongoing\r\n- Owner: ǧ��\r\n- Domain: \r\n- Tags: writing, xuanhuan\r\n\r\n## Current Status\r\n\r\n- Lifecycle: active\r\n- Phase: validation\r\n- Activity: waiting\r\n- Health: yellow\r\n- Delivery: prototype\r\n- Attention: none\r\n- Summary: engineering-leader �ѷ��� 4 �� watched ��������У/������ܹ� QA ��������ɣ������/������ϵ���½� brief/��������ִ��/�ȴ����棬��Ŀ����ṹ����ȱ��֤��\r\n\r\n## Current Focus\r\n\r\nengineering-leader �ѷ��� 4 �� watched ��������У/������ܹ� QA ��������ɣ������/������ϵ���½� brief/��������ִ��/�ȴ����棬��Ŀ����ṹ����ȱ��֤��\r\n\r\n## Project Management Rules\r\n\r\n- Treat `.agent-project/project.json` as the source of truth.\r\n- Use `mycli project-manager status <id>` before continuing work.\r\n- Use `task-add/task-update` for substantial work items.\r\n- Use `next-add/next-update` for immediate next actions or decisions.\r\n- Update project status after meaningful progress or blockers.\r\n- Keep `status.md` generated/readable via project-manager commands.\r\n- For ongoing projects, do not mark as completed; use retired when service stops.\r\n\r\n## Maintenance Rules\r\n\r\n- Prefer small, reversible changes.\r\n- Record decisions in `.agent-project/decisions/` when project direction changes.\r\n- Record dynamic phase context with `context-add` when new assumptions, constraints, architecture notes, validation findings, or operation notes appear.\r\n- For ongoing projects, update operations/runbook and operations context when cadence, trigger, or failure handling changes.\r\n\r\n## Open Tasks\r\n\r\n- task-0002: ��ʵ�� agent ��·��֤������ۡ��½ڡ���У��ܹ� QA [ready, high]\r\n\r\n## Open Next Actions\r\n\r\n- next-0001: ����ʵ agent ��������������� [open, medium]\r\n- next-0002: �ȴ��ĸ� watched builder/QA task-link �ص����������� [open, medium]\r\n\r\n## Dynamic Context for Phase: validation\r\n\r\n- No phase-specific dynamic context recorded yet.\r\n\r\n","exit":0,"description":"Shows project manager agent guide","truncated":false},"title":"Shows project manager agent guide","time":{"start":1777260636637,"end":1777260636764}},"id":"prt_dccfd267f002UQjN2euk2711CY","sessionID":"ses_233033afeffe9G1blGyyhhKVWG","messageID":"msg_dccfd17df0011gQfeEbaqxeKfc"}}
